{"tid":2390273,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[人民公敵］何栢良：大廈有一宗確診個案應即封","createTime":"2021-02-01T12:24:18.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-18T13:33:42.000Z","uid":232237,"like":5,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"cccfc9ad68e5541e33b3275fa0a7f3aa21d9babe","tid":2390273,"uid":232237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T12:24:18.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">何栢良我屌你老母！</span></span></strong><br />\n<strong><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">何栢良我屌你老母！</span></span></strong><br />\n<strong><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">何栢良我屌你老母！</span></span></strong><br />\n<strong><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">何栢良我屌你老母！</span></span></strong><br />\n<strong><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">何栢良我屌你老母！</span></span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/1500p0/0x0/100/st/c3cff6bc27966535cbae3dd9dc5b7700/stheadline/inewsmedia/20210201/_2021020112190966000.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimage.stheadline.com%2Ff%2F1500p0%2F0x0%2F100%2Fst%2Fc3cff6bc27966535cbae3dd9dc5b7700%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20210201%2F_2021020112190966000.jpg&h=e19da04f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/1500p0/0x0/100/st/c3cff6bc27966535cbae3dd9dc5b7700/stheadline/inewsmedia/20210201/_2021020112190966000.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimage.stheadline.com%2Ff%2F1500p0%2F0x0%2F100%2Fst%2Fc3cff6bc27966535cbae3dd9dc5b7700%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20210201%2F_2021020112190966000.jpg&h=e19da04f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/1500p0/0x0/100/st/c3cff6bc27966535cbae3dd9dc5b7700/stheadline/inewsmedia/20210201/_2021020112190966000.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimage.stheadline.com%2Ff%2F1500p0%2F0x0%2F100%2Fst%2Fc3cff6bc27966535cbae3dd9dc5b7700%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20210201%2F_2021020112190966000.jpg&h=e19da04f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n何栢良倡大廈有一宗確診個案即封，並於12小時內完成檢測。 資料圖片<br />\n政府昨晚7時將藍田麗港城第5及第7座列為「受限區域」，封樓進行強制新冠肺炎病毒檢測。行動於今早7時30分完成，約460人接受採樣，當中沒有確診個案，行動中另有60戶無人應門。香港大學感染及傳染病中心總監何栢良批評，麗港城爆疫發生十多日才做封區檢測不及時，建議要走在病毒前，倡每當有大廈出現一宗確診個案，而專家評估該座大廈有高危因素，便應即時封鎖大廈及檢測，非採用現時的「突襲式」封區。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">何栢良我屌你老母！</span></span></strong><br />\n<strong><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">何栢良我屌你老母！</span></span></strong><br />\n<strong><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">何栢良我屌你老母！</span></span></strong><br />\n<strong><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">何栢良我屌你老母！</span></span></strong><br />\n<strong><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">何栢良我屌你老母！</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n何栢良指，最近不少大廈爆發都由地盤群組所致，提議政府於所有確診地盤工人所住大廈都封鎖檢測，料成效可以倍數計。<br />\n<strong><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">何栢良我屌你老母！</span></span></strong><br />\n<strong><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">何栢良我屌你老母！</span></span></strong><br />\n<strong><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">何栢良我屌你老母！</span></span></strong><br />\n<strong><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">何栢良我屌你老母！</span></span></strong><br />\n<strong><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">何栢良我屌你老母！</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n對於政府封麗港城要居民做檢測，何栢良指，加強檢測不論是否找到個案亦有一定作用，惟須視乎時機，他認為，政府新聞稿多次指會盡快識別隔離，但麗港城疫情發生十多日才做封檢太遲，且未有包括全個屋苑。他說，政府欲中斷傳播應「行前幾步」，在病毒傳播之前就推出措施。他舉行指，如每當有大廈出現一宗確診個案，<br />\n<strong><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">何栢良我屌你老母！</span></span></strong><br />\n<strong><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">何栢良我屌你老母！</span></span></strong><br />\n<strong><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">何栢良我屌你老母！</span></span></strong><br />\n<strong><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">何栢良我屌你老母！</span></span></strong><br />\n<strong><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">何栢良我屌你老母！</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n而<strong><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">專家</span></span></strong>評估該座大廈有高危因素，便應即時封鎖大廈及檢測，12小時內完成。<br />\n<br />\n他再次批評政府追蹤不夠快，指近日不少大廈爆發都由地盤群組而引致，認為當中的追蹤工作滯後。他提倡日後應該於所有確診地盤工人所住大廈都封鎖檢測，有陰性結果才放行，料可增加成效以倍計。<br />\n<strong><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">何栢良我屌你老母！</span></span></strong><br />\n<strong><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">何栢良我屌你老母！</span></span></strong><br />\n<strong><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">何栢良我屌你老母！</span></span></strong><br />\n<strong><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">何栢良我屌你老母！</span></span></strong><br />\n<strong><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">何栢良我屌你老母！</span></span></strong><br />\n但他認同，這做法難度較高，因需要同時間去不同地區、大廈做檢測，政府需考慮動員能力。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唔貼link"},{"pid":"fc3f7f03c8ea6aab0ac23ef5d530a2f25bc2db1d","tid":2390273,"uid":232237,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T12:32:02.000Z","msg":"冇人理<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65ec74c0ded27a105d6a2d594c046eb071a3f9a6","tid":2390273,"uid":271669,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T12:34:39.000Z","msg":"何栢良我屌你老母！"},{"pid":"89ded9c6c04abbae40c788d85a97419595aaad37","tid":2390273,"uid":64948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T12:35:52.000Z","msg":"你哋班防疫撚唔係當佢神咁拜㗎咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2cbf97ccb597788667a90a700e085eb57e99235","tid":2390273,"uid":25560,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fc3f7f03c8ea6aab0ac23ef5d530a2f25bc2db1d","tid":2390273,"uid":232237,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T12:32:02.000Z","msg":"冇人理<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T12:35:55.000Z","msg":"個個GME<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c672e2e8b8312d02a9fd98a23b076c8fedbd9ab","tid":2390273,"uid":311480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T12:37:41.000Z",